I'm playing league on a different PC at the very moment. On my other PC, I had unlocked multiple ward skins. I recently bought a bundle that came with a ward skin, and wanting to try it out, I equipped it. The day after, I switched over to this PC because my other had Hard Drive problems. Once I downloaded league on this PC, I wanted to use some of my other wards, but I only saw the option to equip the last ward I had equipped from my other PC, and the default ward. I had looked all around the league client but couldn't find anything that had anything to do with this problem, besides buying other wards, which I was not interested in.


    If anyone could help with this problem, that would great
@AoVo
